messages.content: ComfyUI Profiler is an extension for ComfyUI that calculates the execution time of all nodes.
Who is the developer of ComfyUI Profiler?
The developer of ComfyUI Profiler is tzwm.
What is another extension developed by tzwm for ComfyUI?
Another extension developed by tzwm for ComfyUI is ComfyUI Browser.
Where can one find more information about ComfyUI Browser?
One can find more information about ComfyUI Browser at its GitHub repository: https://github.com/tzwm/comfyui-browser.
Does ComfyUI Profiler provide visual representation of the execution times?
Yes, based on the preview images provided, ComfyUI Profiler displays the execution times of nodes visually in the ComfyUI interface.
How many preview images are provided for ComfyUI Profiler?
There are two preview images provided for ComfyUI Profiler in the given content.
What is the purpose of providing preview images for ComfyUI Profiler?

The purpose of providing preview images for ComfyUI Profiler is to give users a visual representation of how the extension calculates and displays the execution time of nodes within the ComfyUI interface.
